[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has four \Ss, so instead of bidding them she makes a Negative Double.

NORTH knows there is no 8-card fit in \Ss, but he does have \Hs 
stopped. He bids 1NT.

SOUTH has 9 points and with four \Cs she goes back to that suit and NORTH passes.}

